        <p>HVAC contractors who offer customer financing close 47% more deals and increase average ticket sizes by $2,800, according to 2025 industry research. With system replacements averaging $6,500 to $15,000, financing removes the biggest barrier between estimate and signed contract.</p>

        <p>The financing landscape has evolved dramatically. Modern platforms provide instant approvals, seamless software integration, and flexible terms that work for both contractors and customers. Here's how to implement financing that drives revenue growth in 2026.</p>

        <h2 id="financing-impact">How Financing Impacts HVAC Close Rates</h2>

        <p>Contractors using customer financing report these specific improvements:</p>

