          <li><strong>Add-on services:</strong> 156% increase in indoor air quality upgrades</li>
        </ul>

        <p>The psychology is straightforward. A $12,000 system replacement feels overwhelming as a lump sum but becomes manageable at $189 per month over 60 months. Customers focus on monthly payment rather than total cost, making premium equipment and add-ons easier to justify.</p>

        <p>Emergency calls see the biggest impact. When a customer's AC fails in July, they're more likely to approve a complete system upgrade if financing spreads the cost over time. Contractors report 67% close rates on emergency financing versus 34% for cash-only presentations.</p>

