        <h2 id="approval-process">Customer Approval Process</h2>

        <p>Modern HVAC financing takes 2-3 minutes from application to approval. Here's the typical customer experience:</p>

        <ol>
          <li><strong>Application (60 seconds):</strong> Customer provides name, phone, address, and last 4 digits of SSN</li>
          <li><strong>Soft credit check (30 seconds):</strong> Platform checks credit without impacting credit score</li>
          <li><strong>Instant decision (30 seconds):</strong> Customer receives approval amount and terms</li>
          <li><strong>Contract signing (60 seconds):</strong> Electronic signature completes the process</li>
        </ol>

        <p>The soft credit check is crucial. It allows customers to see financing options without damaging their credit score. Only when they accept terms does the platform run a hard credit check to finalize the loan.</p>

        <p>Approval rates vary by credit score ranges:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>720+ credit:</strong> 94% approval rate, lowest interest rates</li>
          <li><strong>660-719 credit:</strong> 78% approval rate, standard rates</li>
          <li><strong>600-659 credit:</strong> 52% approval rate, higher rates or shorter terms</li>
          <li><strong>Below 600:</strong> 23% approval rate, limited to smaller amounts</li>
        </ul>

        <p>For customers with poor credit, some platforms offer co-signer options or alternative approval methods based on income and employment history rather than just credit scores.</p>

